name: 2016 Olio Quattrociocchi Basil
description: The special organic aromatic oils from Olio Quattrociocchi are a must-try. Specially fused with basil during the crushing of the olives, this oil is made exclusively from olives grown on their organic farm in Alatri from the Itrana, Moraiolo, Leccino and Frantoio varieties. Try this oil in your next batch of Pesto or drizzled on tomatoes and grilled vegetables.
